      "name": "Geo Search Point",
      "summary": "The Geo Search Point field allows for capturing and displaying geographic locations with optional search capabilities. It supports rendering a map picker interface for selecting locations and displays search result options if enabled. The field can show a search key label or coordinate-based name, and provides components for editing, embedded display, and atom-style inline presentation. Its primary purpose is to facilitate geolocation data entry and visualization within a card-based system.",
